   "source": [
    "# SmolLM2-360M-Instruct — DRAG Fine-tuning (RAG-aware SFT)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Model**: `HuggingFaceTB/SmolLM2-360M-Instruct`  \n",
    "**Method**: Supervised Fine-tuning (SFT) via TRL `SFTTrainer`  \n",
    "**Dataset**: `training_data_rag.jsonl` (RAG-augmented) produced by `scripts/gen-training-data.mjs --rag`  \n",
    "**Target runtime**: T4 GPU (~2–4 hours)\n",
    "\n",
    "## Steps\n",
    "1. Run the install cell\n",
    "2. Upload `training_data_rag.jsonl` to Google Drive at `ColabDrive/Portfolio/`\n",
    "3. Run remaining cells in order\n",
    "4. Download checkpoint from Drive or use the HF Hub push in Cell 9\n",
    "5. Run ONNX export and quantization cells (Cells 11–12)\n",
    "6. Run the upload cell (Cell 13) to publish ONNX artifacts to HF Hub\n"
   ]
  },
